      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GIN AND JUICE (5) is an honest type in the frame at seven of 29 starts including 15 wins, the latest scoring (16.89) over 300m at Murray Bridge Straight. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Expected to feature in the finish. PAW QWAN (7) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Was a strong winner last time (16.90) over 300m at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 5. Goes very well at the journey winning one races. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. NANGAR LADY (2) could manage only third at this track last time but impressed when posting a slick 19.55 over 342m at Angle Park the start prior. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. OUTSHINE (4) is in the mix after placing last time out.",
